matrixops.maths

Class FractionMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • matrixops.maths.FractionMatrix

  • public class FractionMatrix
extends java.lang.Object
    Matrix data structure with elements represented by Fraction objects. Can perform a number of different matrix operations.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Max Thurell
